<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 via-white to-purple-50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl" data-controller="exercise-checker page-viewer" data-page-viewer-image-url-value="<%= asset_path('nvi5_mat/p030/page.png') %>">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col-reverse sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-2 sm:gap-4">
        <div class="bg-purple-500 text-white text-md sm:text-xl px-2 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 rounded-lg font-bold">
          NUMERI
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-purple-600">LA SOTTRAZIONE</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg sm:text-xl" cursor-pointer hover:bg-purple-700 transition-colors"
           data-action="click->page-viewer#openOriginal"
           title="Clicca per vedere la pagina originale">
        30
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-6">
    <!-- Problema introduttivo -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100 rounded-2xl p-4 md:p-6 border-2 border-blue-200">
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-800 leading-relaxed">
        Il papà di Alessio compra per suo figlio uno skateboard che costa 79,85 euro. Se paga con una banconota da 100 euro, quanto riceve di resto il papà di Alessio?
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Spiegazione -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-purple-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-800 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Per rispondere alla domanda, devi eseguire una sottrazione.<br>
        Ricordi? La sottrazione è l'operazione che serve per <strong class="text-purple-700">calcolare il resto</strong>,
        <strong class="text-purple-700">calcolare quanto manca per completare una quantità</strong> o
        <strong class="text-purple-700">calcolare la differenza tra due quantità</strong>.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-800">
        In questo caso devi eseguire <strong class="text-blue-600 text-xl">100 – 79,85</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Osserva e leggi -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
      <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-purple-700 mb-6">
        • Osserva e leggi
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 md:gap-6">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="bg-purple-50 rounded-xl p-4 border-2 border-purple-200">
          <div class="mb-3">
            <%= image_tag "nvi5_mat/p030/p030_01.jpg", class: "w-full rounded", alt: "Step 1" %>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700 text-center">
            Metti in colonna rispettando il valore posizionale delle cifre.<br>
            <strong class="text-purple-700">Incolonna bene anche le virgole.</strong>
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="bg-purple-50 rounded-xl p-4 border-2 border-purple-200">
          <div class="mb-3">
            <%= image_tag "nvi5_mat/p030/p030_02.jpg", class: "w-full rounded", alt: "Step 2" %>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700 text-center">
            Pareggia le cifre decimali con gli zeri segnaposto.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="bg-purple-50 rounded-xl p-4 border-2 border-purple-200">
          <div class="mb-3">
            <%= image_tag "nvi5_mat/p030/p030_03.jpg", class: "w-full rounded", alt: "Step 3" %>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700 text-center">
            Sottrai le cifre di ogni colonna partendo da destra. Quando il minuendo è minore del sottraendo, esegui il cambio.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6 bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-300 rounded-xl p-4" data-controller="fill-blanks">
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-800">
          Ora puoi rispondere: Il papà di Alessio riceve
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-purple-400 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-purple-600 w-24 text-center font-bold" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="20,15">
          euro di resto.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Esercizi -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-100 to-pink-100 rounded-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-purple-700 mb-6">ESERCIZI</h2>

      <!-- Esercizio 1 -->
      <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <span class="bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">1</span>
          Calcola in colonna sul quaderno.
        </h3>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <!-- Con i numeri interi -->
          <div class="bg-purple-50 rounded-xl p-4">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-purple-700 mb-3">Con i numeri interi</h4>
            <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg">
              <p>795 – 352 =</p>
              <p>6 284 – 2 736 =</p>
              <p>3 742 – 1 508 =</p>
              <p>7 000 – 2 546 =</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Con i numeri decimali -->
          <div class="bg-pink-50 rounded-xl p-4">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-pink-700 mb-3">Con i numeri decimali</h4>
            <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg">
              <p>127 – 6,34 =</p>
              <p>156,03 – 3,07 =</p>
              <p>98,14 – 7,235 =</p>
              <p>2 – 1,755 =</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Esercizio 2 -->
      <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-blue-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="fill-blanks">
        <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">2</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-800 mb-4">
          Lo scorso anno, per comprare le piante di pomodori, Carlo aveva pagato 153 euro. Quest'anno per lo stesso numero di piante ha pagato 189 euro. Quanto ha speso in più quest'anno?
        </p>
        <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-4 mt-4">
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-800">
            <strong>Operazione:</strong> 189 – 153 =
            <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-400 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-600 w-20 text-center font-bold" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="36">
          </p>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-800 mt-3">
            <strong>Risposta:</strong> Carlo ha speso in più
            <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-400 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-600 w-20 text-center font-bold" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="36">
            euro.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Esercizio 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-green-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="fill-blanks">
        <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <span class="bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">3</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-800 mb-4">
          Un puzzle è composto da 300 pezzi. Se Lin ne ha già sistemati 198, quanti pezzi le mancano per terminare?
        </p>
        <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-lg p-4 mt-4">
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-800">
            <strong>Operazione:</strong> 300 – 198 =
            <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-green-400 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-green-600 w-20 text-center font-bold" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="102">
          </p>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-800 mt-3">
            <strong>Risposta:</strong> A Lin mancano
            <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-green-400 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-green-600 w-20 text-center font-bold" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="102">
            pezzi.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer con riferimento -->
    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-red-600 font-bold text-lg">Quaderno esercizi p. 186</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise controls -->
  <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls', color: 'purple' %>
</div>
